{"tid":32403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虎女慘被馬戲團凌虐，獲救後好Hi","createTime":"2016-12-10T07:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T15:00:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c2dcbb8e02ec1ff3c0800360c8ae1e4133a7e6","tid":32403,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481276664_ac94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481276664_ac94.jpg&h=004132c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國德州一個野生動物拯救組織從馬戲團手上救出一隻老虎B女，牠被虐待至皮包骨而且有皮膚病，幸而在飼養員悉心照料，經過長時間治療，老虎女如今已婷婷玉立，更找到了相知相伴的同伴，實在可喜可賀。<br />\n<br />\n孟加拉虎女「Aasha」在2011年3月獲救，當時9個月大的牠只有30磅，相當於正常3個月大老虎的體重。馬戲團的人更迫「Aasha」與其他體型大得多的老虎同住，令瘦小的牠經常被咬。「Aasha」皮膚生癬，多處脫毛，皮膚又乾又裂，嚴重的地方更會出血。<br />\n<br />\n拯救組織創辦人基海（Vicky Keahey）安排「Aasha」入住中心的獨立園區，每日兩次給牠藥、為牠泡藥浴及陪伴牠。8周過去，「Aasha」脫落的毛髮開始再長出來，而本來討厭水的牠亦愛上了玩水。<br />\n<br />\n8個月後「Aasha」終於「似隻老虎」，組織於是安排牠認識園內其他老虎，結果與同病相憐的雄虎「Smuggler」一見如故，基海說：「我們安排Aasha與Smuggler毗鄰而居，Smuggler簡直為牠瘋狂，努力吸引牠的注意。」<br />\n<br />\n組織於是撮合「Aasha」及「Smuggler」住在一起，兩虎如今已「交往」4年，感情十分好。從「Aasha」幸福的表情看來，就知道牠對如今的生活非常滿意。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481276667_3d62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481276667_3d62.jpg&h=6653e7c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98dd228b03c384aceb872793e1bd3bab48dac3c8","tid":32403,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f883f046d1a3d939174089e1f27077ee7b5f1a","tid":32403,"uid":36862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"連隻老虎都過得幸福過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec6b59035245193f83c70cf19175ee5c15f7fae","tid":32403,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連隻老虎都過得幸福過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幸福與否在乎心態"},{"pid":"d784ea438c2ea3ce21b76ea90571515f66edf886","tid":32403,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連隻老虎都過得幸福過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幸福與否在乎心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早打繁體字咪好囉，之前啲人好憎你"},{"pid":"add6240acdd8b187d31a5763458ff9a2c7f9004f","tid":32403,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"個馬戲團係咪美國當地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbd8b5d3bce7610e0482e32d27ac30ee171700a","tid":32403,"uid":61057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"睇咗做處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c70bbb9f2aebb93d71b9af787de4aeb8b9120b6","tid":32403,"uid":24453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"意為白虎"},{"pid":"3c717e9392c5c0d0ddbfe0bc2b10284f9614837e","tid":32403,"uid":8510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"有啲馬戲團真喺好衰 會虐待動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實老虎真喺幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed3e341241f13c6fdcea7293baf14f3c7ff5540","tid":32403,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply